{"type": "article", "id": 39893, "title": "这个借鉴变色龙的腕表，想把时间藏起来｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-04-17T23:05:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 39582, "name": "Anicorn Watches"}, {"id": 39583, "name": "BOUD"}, {"id": 39584, "name": "福永纸工"}, {"id": 35864, "name": "大口进也"}, {"id": 39585, "name": "Chicco Chiari"}, {"id": 39586, "name": "Jessica Dance"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 341, "image": "img/article/article_show/201704172208032KszctEw8uYNW9iM.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Hidden Time Watch by Anicorn Watches</h3><p>在成功完成了两款手表的众筹项目之后，香港手表品牌 Anicorn Watches 决定推出一条名为 Trio of Time 的产品线，与三位来自不同城市的设计师联手打造三款具有独特风格手表。这款名为 Hidden Time 的腕表由来自韩国首尔的工业设计师 Jiwoong Jung 参与设计，它最特别的地方在于非常规的时针：为了将时间隐藏起来，他借鉴了自然界中变色龙的防御机制，通过不断旋转的渐变色表面将尚未到来的时间和刻度没入一片素净的白色之中。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/221213970/hidden-time-watch\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 1199 港币。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417222954gE1VnMFkT4ymZiYq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220917EpQXaY0TPfItjrRN.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.461765\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220917SljBEqWtCpvs2NLb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220917esvWnoz5Mr9Eg6OZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220917u0wO8NFbZlTYAEh3.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220917kaPFfSDzQ6MAyLiJ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>PLUB by BOUD</h3><p>对市面上的无线耳机不感冒，或者是设备没有传统的耳机接口，因此想把有线耳机直接改成无线版不需要你大费周折了。来自美国加州的设计公司 BOUD 最近推出了一款名为 PLUB 的转换器，仅重 10 克的它看起来就像是一块积木，使用时只要把有线耳机插入 3.5 mm 接口即可。除此之外，它还有一个配套的颈带，可以将耳机线连同 PLUB 一起收纳起来，提升了便携性。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/864001667/plub-dont-plug-in-plub-in\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，含颈带的套装售价为 27 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220942osnD5w6Aecg3uXvm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220942eB5UoEchiLmX4Pau.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.176471\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pleats and Box Clock by Shinya Oguchi</h3><p>在今年的米兰设计周期间，日本设计师<a href=\"http://www.shinyaoguchi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">大口进也</a>在专门展示设计领域最新发展的 <a href=\"http://www.venturaprojects.com/ventura-lambrate-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ventura Lambrate</a> 展区内展示了自己和印刷公司<a href=\"http://www.fukunaga-print.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">福永纸工</a>联手打造的拉伸型置物架 <a href=\"http://www.shinyaoguchi.com/shelf\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pleats</a> 和时钟 <a href=\"http://www.shinyaoguchi.com/tableclock\" rel=\"nofollow\">Box Clock</a>，这两款产品都是以纸板为原材料制作而成的。尽管纸板的厚度只有 0.7 毫米，但蛇腹式的折叠结构让 Pleats 能够承受书本等重物，不需要时还能折叠起来节省空间。Box Clock 则是由两个纸板厚度为 2 毫米的盒子组合而成的，外部用来固定的订书钉同时起到了装饰的效果，体现出一种朴素的美感。目前这两件产品仍处于打样阶段，还未投入大规模生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704172209587qmDWKhpZTJNratb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220957j2nbQiVlJWrkHc3Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669136\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220958aJcgx84XZ3wfN9ko.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666400\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220957W7YvSkazjx3y2TFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669136\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220957m5ltIfx0dFMXi2nL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220958LXe0xjcFRbD2Zgdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fantasmini by Chicco Chiari</h3><p>让人暴露年龄的经典电子游戏也是很多设计师的灵感来源，来自意大利的 <a href=\"http://www.chiccochiari.it/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chicco Chiari</a> 最近就把《吃豆人》中的幽灵打造成了一套名为 Fantasmini 的灯饰。不过，和其它类似“衍生设计”不同的是，Chiari 并没有用上塑料或是其它能让人回到 1980 年代的材质，而是选择了拥有浅灰色细纹的卡拉拉大理石（Carrara），以营造出一种独特的通透感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221054M8q3LHBuJs2bi0KP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686719\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221054zZHsTo941RltWCpD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221054D7MsUul5WOGb340v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221054BYRNWln32U9PmAKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.904938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221055GijZPInKNJhUpys3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658025\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Atlas Coffee Club</h3><p>谁不想在收到一袋精选咖啡豆的同时通过精美的包装让眼睛也能感受到异域之美呢？<a href=\"https://atlascoffeeclub.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Atlas Coffee Club</a> 是一个来自美国的咖啡订阅服务，由于每个月他们会给用户邮寄一袋来自某个国家的咖啡豆，设计师便以原产地特有的艺术风格为灵感设计了包装袋正面的图案，将 logo 和产品的具体信息安排在了袋子的两侧和背面，让顾客在不被影响的情况下更直观地感受异域风情。当袋子逐渐增多，在架子上一字排开又起到了装饰效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221303A1fYTGoReWh8S4sJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.648000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221304f3Gda90QNyA8lDEH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704172213047Uig1MKbWynh5uDO.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221304PbLxHv0eJzqcEgCU.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.875000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417221303Xl1ijpnCBq4c9TFm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.874000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bad Eggs by Jessica Dance</h3><p>以制作各类羊毛毡模型闻名的英国艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.jessicadance.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jessica Dance</a> 为上周末的复活节制作了一套名为 Bad Eggs 的羊毛毡彩蛋，从一语双关的名称中就能看出她是想借此嘲讽那些只会对自己的人民开出空头支票、给予虚假承诺的坏蛋们，用幽默的方式提醒人们即使在和平年代也不要忘记某些领袖所缺失的特质——尽管被简化到没有具体的表情只有标志性的发型和胡须，你还是能够认出这三只坏蛋指的是谁。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220859qlSuC7UBrLFaAk5w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170417220858sP7y8gbwa3fDFmdS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704172208583RISgXZ0EW4jVYac.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}